0= \frac{x}{p}-\frac{n-x}{1-p}\rightarrow \frac{x}{p}=\frac{n-x}{1-p}\rightarrow \frac{1-p}{p}=\frac{n-x}{x}\rightarrow \frac{1}{p}=\frac{n}{x}\rightarrow \hat p=\frac{x}{n}
